The Kiss concert at the legendary Budokan Hall from October 24th, broadcasted by WOWOW.
Unfortunately, no Full HD master have pop out yet from the rising sun earth, so i been forced to work with the 720p file from jpfiles (for the record, NO YTBE SOURCED), so the quality it's not best (yeah, i know...) but very watchable, so still worthy for give it a shot. All that said, i did my best on this disc considerating the quality handicaps from the source, removing almost 30 minutes (!) of useless footage and making a DVD9 transfer for avoid as much as possible pixelation.
IMPORTANT: IF A FULL HD MASTER OR BETTER SOURCE POP OUT, PLEASE LET ME KNOW AND I WILL PROUDLY REDO (I hope that some of our japanese members could bring us a definitive version of this show).
